## How Peer Review Connects to Quality Tiers

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Contributor initiates review cycle] --> B[Cycle opens for target tier]
    B --> C[L3+ reviewers submit structured reviews]
    C --> D{Min reviews reached?}
    D -->|No| C
    D -->|Yes| E[Auto-close cycle + calculate consensus]
    E --> F{Consensus?}
    F -->|Yes - meets standard| G[Auto-advance tier via assess_quality_tier RPC]
    F -->|Split / Needs work| H[Tier stays, feedback visible]
    G --> I[+rep to reviewers aligned with consensus]
    H --> I
    I --> J[Reviewers see alignment feedback]
```

